    <section id="thecourses" class="container thecourses"> 
     <h2>My Favorite Course</h2> 
     <blockquote>
      <p>“Our professor pushed us and pushed us. In a very loving way, of course. It gave me the feeling that I could be a French major.”</p>
     </blockquote> 
     <p class="name"><strong>Adijat Mustapha,</strong> on Intermediate French</p> 
    </section> 
